name: 무제 하나 첫 번째 - untitled 1 (1).bmp - Meta Space Object
description:
Meta 3d version of an object of the "bmp abstract expressionist collection", first made in vietnam, with a little help of my friend Hyo Jung Kim that borrowed her computer for me to use the old version of Wiondows Paint.

8 years later i revisited the image, with new version of this old app, Paint 3D, that make the transition from simple picture media, to this meta space object
